                  <provenance> '<persName role="sgn" key="person_3520">Rich. Wills</persName>' (16th cent.) is on the old cover (fol. 161).</provenance>
                  <provenance><persName role="fmo" key="person_68971787">Thomas Percy, 1729-1811, Bishop of Dromore, collector of ballads</persName>; his sale, Sotheby's, 29 April 1884 (lot 83) </provenance>
